Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.84,0:00:26.62,EN,,0,0,0,,We have terms like dousei aisha which means
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.62,0:00:29.27,EN,,0,0,0,,somebody who likes somebody from the same gender,
